This web application is based on the hosted ArcGIS Online map tour template. The application depicts NAIP imagery coverage starting in 2002 and ending in 2014. The information contained in the JPEG images contained in the tour was aquired from historical archives of imagery coverage at the Aerial Photography Field Office. Notation of change and highlights for each year was also derived from historical contracting sources at the Aerial Photography Field Office.</dct:description>
